import React from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemIcon,
  ListItemText,
  Divider,
  Box
} from '@mui/material';
import EcoIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Eco';
import RecyclingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Recycling';
import LocalShippingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocalShipping';
import BusinessIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Business';
import HandshakeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Handshake';

const AboutPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 4 }}>
      <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" align="center" gutterBottom>
        About AgriWaste Market
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" align="center" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        Connecting farmers and businesses for sustainable waste management
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Our Mission
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                AgriWaste Market is dedicated to creating a sustainable ecosystem where agricultural waste is transformed into valuable resources. We connect farmers with businesses that can utilize agricultural byproducts, reducing environmental impact while creating economic opportunities.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Our Vision
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                We envision a world where agricultural waste is no longer seen as a problem but as a valuable resource. Through our platform, we aim to create a circular economy in agriculture, where waste is minimized, resources are maximized, and sustainable practices are the norm.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
            Key Features
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                    <EcoIcon color="primary" sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6">Sustainable Solutions</Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="body2">
                    Connect with verified buyers and sellers of agricultural waste products.
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                    <RecyclingIcon color="primary" sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6">Waste Management</Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="body2">
                    Efficiently manage and track your agricultural waste products.
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                    <LocalShippingIcon color="primary" sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6">Logistics Support</Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="body2">
                    Access to reliable transportation and logistics services.
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                    <BusinessIcon color="primary" sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6">Business Growth</Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="body2">
                    Expand your business by connecting with new markets and opportunities.
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                    <HandshakeIcon color="primary" sx={{ mr: 1 }} />
                    <Typography variant="h6">Community</Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="body2">
                    Join a network of like-minded individuals and businesses.
                  </Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Our Impact
              </Typography>
              <List>
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <EcoIcon color="primary" />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="1000+ Tons of Waste Processed"
                    secondary="Reducing environmental impact"
                  />
                </ListItem>
                <Divider />
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <BusinessIcon color="primary" />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="500+ Verified Sellers"
                    secondary="Creating economic opportunities"
                  />
                </ListItem>
                <Divider />
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <HandshakeIcon color="primary" />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="95% Customer Satisfaction"
                    secondary="Building trust and reliability"
                  />
                </ListItem>
              </List>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default AboutPage;
